additional_info:
To change the color of the purple override, go down to the second section of code, at the very top there will be something that looks like this:

:root {
--c1: #7976BB;
}

Replace that one instance of #7976BB and everything should change to the color you want, you still have to have the purple display color chosen though, if you choose another color on the twitter settings your chosen color will <i>not</i> be displayed.

